<template>
  <cus-wraper>
    <el-form :inline="true" :model="params" class="demo-ruleForm" label-width="auto"
             style="margin-left: 30px">
      <el-row>
        <el-col :span="8">
          <el-form-item :label="$t('disease.diseaseType')">
            <el-input v-model="params.disTypeCode" clearable/>
          </el-form-item>
        </el-col>
        <el-col :span="8">
          <el-form-item :label="$t('disease.diseaseEdition')">
            <el-input v-model="params.disEdition" clearable/>
          </el-form-item>
        </el-col>
        <el-col :span="8">
          <el-form-item :label="$t('disease.diseaseName')">
            <el-input v-model="params.disName" clearable/>
          </el-form-item>
        </el-col>
      </el-row>

      <el-row>
        <el-col :span="24" align="left">
          <el-button icon='el-icon-search' size="small" style="width: 130px" type="primary" @click="doSearch()">
            {{ $t('table.search') }}
          </el-button>
        </el-col>
      </el-row>

    </el-form>

    <cus-table-title :label="$t('disease.disease')"/>

    <el-table :data="configs1" align="center" border class="wraper-table" element-loading-text="Loading" fit
              highlight-current-row
              size="mini">
      <el-table-column :label="$t('table.id')" align="center">
        <template v-slot="scope">
          {{ initTableIndex('page', scope.$index) }}
        </template>
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('disease.diseaseType')" align="center"
                       prop="disTypeCode"></el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('disease.diseaseEdition')" align="center"
                       prop="disEdition"></el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('disease.diseaseCode')" align="center"
                       prop="disCode"></el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('disease.diseaseName')" align="center"
                       prop="disName"></el-table-column>
      <el-table-column :label="$t('table.actions')" align="center">
        <template v-slot="scope">
          <el-button icon="el-icon-connection" size="mini" type="primary" @click="selectRow(scope.row)">
            {{ $t('form.select') }}
          </el-button>
        </template>
      </el-table-column>

    </el-table>
    <cus-pagination ref="page" v-model="configs1" :pageSize="5" :params="params"
                    url="/claim-test/base/queryDisClass"/>


  </cus-wraper>
</template>
<script>

let _this
export default {
  name: 'disease',
  filters: {},
  data() {
    _this = this
    return {
      configs1: [],
      params: {
        disTypeCode: '',
        disEdition: '',
        disName: ''
      }
    }
  },
  computed: {},
  mounted() {
  },
  created() {

  },
  methods: {
    doSearch() {
      this.$refs.page.reload()
    },
    selectRow(row) {
      this.$emit('select', row)
    }
  }
}
</script>
<style lang="scss" scoped>


</style>
